photo.caption: American Legation - another view from balcony

data.ranking_subcategory: #1 of 49 things to do in Tangier
data.subcategory_ranking: #1 of 49 things to do in Tangier
data.ranking: #1 of 49 things to do in Tangier
data.description: The American Legation in Tangier is the only US Historic Monument located outside American soil. It hosts the Tangier American Legation Institute for Moroccan Studies (TALIM). TALIM includes, among others, a private museum, a research library accessible by appointment only, and a community Arabic Literacy Program. Admission fee is: * MAD 20 per person for Moroccan citizens and foreigners resident in Morocco, * MAD 50 for non-resident foreigners. * Free admission for Children under 12. * Guided tours available for MAD 100 per person. Opening hours are: * Monday - Friday: 10:00 am - 5:00 pm * Saturday: 10:00 am - 3:00 pm.
